152	/// `%(trailers:key=...)` placeholder. Git only recognises the *last* paragraph
153	/// of a message as the trailer block, so a blank line between two trailers
154	/// makes every trailer above it invisible. Release commit
155	/// 59650f2b45ebebf29ed67d33c9a19c1e82e7c003 separated its `Formal-AI-Session`
156	/// and `Formal-AI-Evidence` trailers with a blank line, git reported only the
157	/// evidence trailer, and the resulting "must record both" error failed the
158	/// whole Auto Release job (issue #796).
